        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You have an object that comforts you, such as a favorite rock, a childhood stuffed animal, or another trinket. While you hold your personal trinket, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus on saving throws and to Will DCs against fear effects. If your personal trinket is ever lost or destroyed, you can gain another one by spending 1 week of downtime searching for a suitable replacement.</p>\n<p>Additionally, you gain the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Self Soothe] action.</p>"
